Instructions:

1. Get the current version of Delphes - http://cmssw.cvs.cern.ch/cgi-bin/cmssw.cgi/UserCode/spadhi/Snowmass/Delphes/
2. tar -zxf Delphes-3.0.6.tar.gz
3. cd Delphes-3.0.6
4. make
5. Get pileup files from: 

http://red-gridftp11.unl.edu/Snowmass/MinBias13TeV.tar.gz
http://red-gridftp11.unl.edu/Snowmass/MinBias33TeV.tar.gz

tar -zxf MinBias13TeV.tar.gz
mv MinBias13TeV.pileup MinBias.pileup 

6. One can get the card files from http://cmssw.cvs.cern.ch/cgi-bin/cmssw.cgi/UserCode/spadhi/Snowmass/Cards/
 a) delphes_card_Snowmass_NoPileUp.tcl
 b) delphes_card_Snowmass_50PileUp.tcl
 c) delphes_card_Snowmass_140PileUp.tcl
 copy the tcl file to Delphes-3.0.6/examples/delphes_card_Snowmass_NoPileUp.tcl
 copy the tcl file to Delphes-3.0.6/examples/delphes_card_Snowmass_50PileUp.tcl
 copy the tcl file to Delphes-3.0.6/examples/delphes_card_Snowmass_140PileUp.tcl

6. Use your favourate Physics model:
 ./DelphesHepMC examples/delphes_card_Snowmass_NoPileUp.tcl ttbar_NOPU.root GenEvent_ASCII.hepmc
 ./DelphesHepMC examples/delphes_card_Snowmass_50PileUp.tcl ttbar_50PU.root GenEvent_ASCII.hepmc
 ./DelphesHepMC examples/delphes_card_Snowmass_140PileUp.tcl ttbar_140PU.root GenEvent_ASCII.hepmc
 


